## ğŸ¨ DESIGN SYSTEM

### Colors
- Primary: `#FFD700` (Gold)
- Background: `#000000` (Black)
- Text: `#FFFFFF` (White)
- Success: `#00FF00` (Green)
- Error: `#FF0000` (Red)

### Typography
- Headers: System fonts
- Body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI"
- Code: "Courier New", monospace

### Breakpoints
- Mobile: < 768px
- Tablet: 768px - 1024px
- Desktop: > 1024px

